reviews:
Sangeetha Restaurant delivers on the most important fronts: delicious, generous portions of food at very reasonable prices, making it a great choice for families. While some operational issues and a safety concern arose during a busy time, the overall experience remains strongly positive. A great spot for a satisfying and value-filled meal.
Kids Masala Dosa;
Absolutely fantastic! The dosa was perfectly crispy and had a delicious, authentic taste. The portion was huge—much bigger than expected for a kids' menu item priced at just $7.99 CAD. My son loved it, and it was easily enough to share. Gr
